ESPORTS WORLD CUP ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ko epic conclusion ko lagi stage set cha! After weeks of breath-taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it ‚Äî EWC ma 2025 PMWC ko last matches. World ko best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion‚Äôs share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Harek rotation, harek zone ra harek elimination le aja pura championship ko outcome change garna sakcha kinaki, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

Group stage ra Survival Stage ko unforgettable journey pachi, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

üî•SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
The top 16 teams on one stage ‚Äî no second chances!
Every match counts in the race for the championship!
Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
Explosive SMASH RULE format ‚Äî pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

üìÖ TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
Group Stage: July 25‚Äì27
Survival Stage: July 29‚Äì30
Grand Finals: August 1‚Äì3

Try PUBG MOBILE now: https://pubgmobile.live/2025PMWC

YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: [NP] 2025 PMWC at EWC Grand Finals D3 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
ESPORTS WORLD CUP ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ko epic conclusion ko lagi stage set cha! After weeks of breath-taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it ‚Äî EWC ma 2025 PMWC ko last matches. World ko best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion‚Äôs share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Harek rotation, harek zone ra harek elimination le aja pura championship ko outcome change garna sakcha kinaki, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

Group stage ra Survival Stage ko unforgettable journey pachi, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

üî•SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- The top 16 teams on one stage ‚Äî no second chances!
- Every match counts in the race for the championship!
- Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
- Explosive SMASH RULE format ‚Äî pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

üìÖ TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
Group Stage: July 25‚Äì27

Harek rotation, harek zone ra harek elimination le aja pura championship ko outcome change garna sakcha kinaki, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

Group stage ra Survival Stage ko unforgettable journey pachi, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

üî•SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

ESPORTS WORLD CUP ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ko epic conclusion ko lagi stage set cha! After weeks of breath-taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it ‚Äî EWC ma 2025 PMWC ko last matches. World ko best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion‚Äôs share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Harek rotation, harek zone ra harek elimination le aja pura championship ko outcome change garna sakcha kinaki, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

Group stage ra Survival Stage ko unforgettable journey pachi, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

üî•SMASH RULE le kasari kaam garcha?
Grand Finals ko Day 2 pachi match point threshold lai #1 rank ma raheko team ko points +10 ma set garine cha. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals - winning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If kunai pani teams le Match 18 samma ma SMASH RULE bata title secure garena bhane the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
The top 16 teams on one stage ‚Äî no second chances!
Every match counts in the race for the championship!
Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
Explosive SMASH RULE format ‚Äî pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: [EN] 2025 PMWC at EWC Grand Finals D3 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
üèÜ GRAND FINALS DAY 3 | AUGUST 3

The stage is set for the epic conclusion of the 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP! After weeks of breath taking competition, today marks the final day of the Grand Finals in Riyadh, where one team will rise above the rest to claim the crown and secure their place in PUBG MOBILE history.

This is it ‚Äî the last matches of 2025 PMWC at EWC. The world‚Äôs best 16 teams have given everything, but only one will lift the trophy and take home the lion‚Äôs share of the $3,000,000 prize pool. Every rotation, every zone, and every elimination today could change the outcome of the entire championship because, now a team can win with SMASH RULE.

After an unforgettable journey through the Group Stage and the Survival Stage, today we crown the champion of 2025 PMWC at EWC.

üî• How does SMASH RULE work? 
On the last day of the 2025 PMWC Grand Finals, we have the Match Point Threshold! In Overall Ranking after 12th match, #1 ranked team‚Äôs points +10. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy‚Äîwinning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If no team secures the title via SMASH Rule by Match 18, the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- The top 16 teams on one stage ‚Äî no second chances!
- Every match counts in the race for the championship!
- Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
- Explosive SMASH RULE format ‚Äî pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!
